<paragraph blockId="81.[172,1380,1750,3044]" box="[172,1096,2735,2768]" pageId="81" pageNumber="358">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[172,407,2735,2768]" pageId="81" pageNumber="358">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Probably similar to the White-throated Woodrat.
</paragraph>
